			    <HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  	For each planet with Military Bases:<br />
<br />
MP = Bases * (10 + Military CM for that planet)<br />
<br />
The above assumes that you have enough population to man all the bases (that is why it is necessary to never run out of PP in the planet investment pool - I tend to keep 1000 turns worth of funding in the pool if I can afford it just in case I can't get back to the game for a few days).			   <P align=right></P>
